Class MinTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.BaseAggregateFunction

        • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.MinTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AggregateFunction, TemporalAggregateFunction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MinEdgeTime, MinVertexTime

    public class MinTime
extends AbstractTimeAggregateFunction
    Base class for calculating the minimum of a field of a time-interval for temporal elements. If a valid time attribute is used for aggregation, this function ignores the default values (TemporalElement.DEFAULT_TIME_FROM and TemporalElement.DEFAULT_TIME_TO) and handles it the same way as null.
